@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
        <p class="lead">Embark on a Journey Through Privacy</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card mt-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <p>Welcome to the mystical realms of the Team Management Privacy Policy!</p>
            
            <p>Your magical privacy is of utmost importance to us. This enchanted document reveals how we gather, employ, and safeguard your information in our mystical Team Management application.</p>
            
            <h2 class="mt-4">The Secrets We Gather</h2>
            <p>We weave the fabric of destiny using the information we collect:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Your mystic name and ethereal contact information</li>
                <li>Whispers of team and project details</li>
                <li>Chronicles of communication history</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h2 class="mt-4">Unveiling the Power of Your Information</h2>
            <p>We harness your information to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Wield the magic of effective team and project management</li>
                <li>Facilitate telepathic communication among team members</li>
                <li>Amplify the enchantments of our application's features and capabilities</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h2 class="mt-4">A Pledge of Non-Divulgence</h2>
            <p>We honor your privacy and never reveal your personal secrets to third parties without your mystical consent.</p>
            
            <h2 class="mt-4">Warding Off Dark Forces</h2>
            <p>We cast powerful protective spells to shield your information from unauthorized access and malevolent forces.</p>
            
            <h2 class="mt-4">Empowerment of Choice</h2>
            <p>Feel free to wield your own magic and update or vanish your information from our mystical scrolls whenever you desire.</p>
            
            <h2 class="mt-4">Contact the Keepers</h2>
            <p>If you seek counsel or have questions about our arcane privacy practices, commune with us at <a href="mailto:privacy@teammanagement.com">privacy@teammanagement.com</a>.</p>
            
            <p class="text-center mt-4">May the stars guide you on your journey with Team Management!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
